assignee: codex-root
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: Published package is available through npm/npx and Bun/bunx
goal: lossless-automatic-releases
objective: verified-package-publication
value: Provide one trustworthy package artifact to both ecosystems.
impact: Avoids duplicate publication and catches broken Bun consumption.
outcome: Each release tag maps to one verified npm artifact and GitHub release.
why_now: The user requires correct npm and Bun publication behavior.
